{
  "name": "RPlog_Ariana_Millikin_and_Company",
  "title": "Ariana Millikin and Company",
  "summary": "At the main spaceport of Calamari's Coral City, the retired General Lando Calrissian, frustrated with supply troubles for his Nkllon operation, spots the weary and standoffish Ariana Millikin and lays on his trademark charm to lift her spirits. Their flirtation is interrupted by the arrival of the businessman Talon Karrde, with whom Lando trades barbed banter about smuggling, the defeated Empire, and Karrde's new gambling venture on Caspar. Lando secures a table for two at Karrde's casino for himself and Ariana before hurrying off to a supplier meeting. Left alone with Karrde, Ariana drops her guard and quietly pleads to leave with him, hinting at a deeper history between them. Karrde firmly refuses, citing unacceptable risk, and turns back to inspect his ship, leaving a resigned Ariana to walk away in the opposite direction.",
